                    true of most writers or did you find <span class="unclear tooltip" title="Text was unclear">[something else true]</span>?</p>
<p><span class="speaker">William Faulkner</span>Well, it is not true of&mdash;of me, and I imagine it's not true
                    of&mdash;of many other writers. It would be true of&mdash;would be true
                    of&mdash;of many other writers. I think that&mdash;that Maugham,
                    of an older&mdash;older culture, had more time to be that
