<p><span class="speaker">William Faulkner</span>Yes, sir.</p>
<p><span class="speaker">Unidentified participant</span>I hesitate to ask such a broad question, sir, but what effect do you
                    think McCarthyism has had on freedom of thought and expression in American
                    universities?</p>
<p><span class="speaker">William Faulkner</span>I would say that&mdash;that McCarthyism, that whole thing, has had a
